actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Agriculture.

official_title: A bill to adjust target prices established under the Agriculture and Consumer Protection Act of 1973, as amended, for the 1974 through 1977 crops of wheat and feed grains to reflect changes in farm production costs.

summary.text: Revises the Agriculture and Consumer Protection Act by adjusting the method of computation of price support payments for the 1974 through 1977 crops of wheat and feed grains to reflect changes in farm production costs.

titles.title: A bill to adjust target prices established under the Agriculture and Consumer Protection Act of 1973, as amended, for the 1974 through 1977 crops of wheat and feed grains to reflect changes in farm production costs.
